      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BULL MARKET (4) was a strong winner (29.48) from box 2 last time, scoring by 8 lengths at this track. Has a tricky draw to overcome and will need a clean break. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can make it back-to-back wins. CYCLONE ETHICS (2) jumped from an outside draw and finished in the frame when a 2.5 lengths second (22.49) at Bulli in Grade 4/5. Is yet to find the frame here from three. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Winning chance. GALBA MAJOR (7) has missed the frame at his last two runs but could not have been more impressive the run prior in his exceptional 29.55 win at this track over 520m. Smart winner three back and looks a key chance on that form. BLUE FRANKY (8) is worth some thought after placing last start.",
